This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-caam-pkc-sec layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Maintainer: Marouene Boubakri <marouene.boubakri@nxp.com>

To add the meta-caam-pkc-sec layer to your build

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-caam-pkc-sec'

Please refer to the Application Note AN12838 for assistance on building and using Public Key Cryptography using CAAM Secure Key demo.
